abstracts.cdata!:
The project would assist in financing
            (i) the construction of highways in Slovenia, Macedonia and
            Kosovo, and (ii) the purchase of engineering equipment,
            consulting services and staff training abroad to help
            Republics and Provinces improve highway planning,
            administration and project preparation.
